Dialogue: 2,1:28:41.89,1:28:43.85,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Ellie: What the hell are you doing here?
Dialogue: 2,1:28:45.84,1:28:47.90,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Jesse: Think I'd let you do this on your own?
Dialogue: 2,1:33:44.37,1:33:47.53,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Ellie: Why did you pull me out of there while I still unconscious?
Dialogue: 2,1:33:50.32,1:33:52.95,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Joel: Because I let them run their tests,
Dialogue: 2,1:33:53.36,1:33:56.36,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,and when I saw that they were useless, I got us out of there--
Dialogue: 2,1:33:56.36,1:33:58.36,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Ellie: How do you know they were useless?
Dialogue: 2,1:33:58.36,1:34:02.36,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you just woulda given them more time, they could have figured something out--
Dialogue: 2,1:34:00.71,1:34:02.50,辉英 Script,,0,0,90,,Joel: Ellie!
Dialogue: 2,1:34:04.90,1:34:08.87,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,There was no cure.
Dialogue: 2,1:34:12.28,1:34:16.68,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that could've helped these people or anybody else.
Dialogue: 2,1:34:20.27,1:34:23.98,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,I know you wish things were different -- I wish things were different.
Dialogue: 2,1:34:25.53,1:34:26.62,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,But they ain't.
Dialogue: 2,2:02:10.94,2:02:12.37,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Ellie: Oh no!
Dialogue: 2,2:02:12.37,2:02:14.15,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 2,2:02:15.28,2:02:16.81,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Jesus.
Dialogue: 2,2:02:18.36,2:02:20.05,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 2,2:02:31.26,2:02:32.98,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 2,2:02:35.36,2:02:36.98,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Stupid dog.
Dialogue: 2,2:26:39.92,2:26:42.93,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, since you ask so nicely…
Dialogue: 2,2:26:43.36,2:26:44.66,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Get the ball!
Dialogue: 2,2:26:47.34,2:26:49.14,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Sorry buddy. My bad.
Dialogue: 2,2:33:35.70,2:33:38.31,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Mel: It's kind of hard to imagine you being afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 2,2:33:38.31,2:33:40.55,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Abby: I'm not as fearless as you think.
Dialogue: 2,2:33:40.55,2:33:41.64,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Mel: Oh please.
Dialogue: 2,2:33:41.64,2:33:44.76,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Abby: Like I could never do the surgery stuff you do.
Dialogue: 2,2:33:44.76,2:33:47.30,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,I'd be too freaked out about fucking it up.
Dialogue: 2,2:33:47.59,2:33:49.76,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Mel: You think I don't feel the same way?
Dialogue: 2,2:33:49.76,2:33:53.96,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Abby: Well, for what it's worth my dad always said you were his best student.
Dialogue: 2,2:33:54.35,2:33:55.47,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Mel: He did?
Dialogue: 2,2:33:55.92,2:33:59.26,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,Well… you always said he was an idiot.
Dialogue: 2,2:34:00.04,2:34:00.91,辉英 Script,,0,0,0,,C'mon.
